            "value": {
              "markup": "<p><span>This member is already added to this research ethics committee.</span></p>\n<p><span>If you need to change the research ethics committee assigned to this member, you can do so by going to their user profile.</span></p>\n<p><span>To get help, contact the support team.&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><strong>Online<br></strong>Visit the <a rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://healthresearchauthority.haloitsm.com/portal\" target=\"_blank\">HRA support site</a></p>\n<p><strong>Email<br></strong><a href=\"mailto:service.desk@hra.nhs.uk\">service.desk@hra.nhs.uk</a></p>\n<p><strong>Phone<br></strong>020 7104 8260<br>Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm</p>",
